name: Mayfair
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
What is the project about? DTF trading platform on arbitrum


What makes your project unique? Mayfair allows to to trade narratives rather than coins/tokens due to their DTF platform. This allows users to play/trade the market in a different way than they normally would.  Mayfair is one of the only places a user can trade using DTFs and the project is actively adding more DTFs to trade. 


History of your project. Launched on array capital launchpad and project is now live, TGE was 5/23/2023


What’s next for your project? Supporting more DTFs


What can your token be used for? Platform usage
